## Data & model attribution

This repository bundles or loads data derived from the following sources.
These sources retain their original licenses and terms of use, which are
NOT overridden by the MIT license on the software itself:

- European Social Survey Round 11 (ESS11) microdata — © ESS ERIC.
  Use subject to the ESS Data Policy (https://www.europeansocialsurvey.org/data/).
  Downloaded files in `data/ESS11*.csv` and derivatives in
  `data/ess_clean.parquet` are redistributed here under the ESS research-use
  conditions; downstream users must register with ESS before re-distribution.
- Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3 model weights — © Mistral AI, released under the
  Apache 2.0 license. Not redistributed in this repository; loaded at runtime
  from Hugging Face.
